OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA mostly dry and bright morning
OL,6,Fwith some hazy sunny spells. Turning
OL,7,Fcloudier through the afternoon for
OL,8,FOrkney with the odd spot of rain, but
OL,9,Fremaining mainly dry for Shetland.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FA rather cloudy evening with
OL,12,Fsome late brightness for Shetland, but
OL,13,Foutbreaks of rain soon arriving for
OL,14,FOrkney. Rain turns heavy for a time as
OL,15,Fit spreads to Shetland overnight.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
