OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CWednesday:FA cloudy and wet start for
OL,6,FShetland, but drier and brighter for
OL,7,FOrkney. Sunny spells developing as
OL,8,Frain clears Shetland, but a few
OL,9,Fafternoon showers developing for
OL,10,FOrkney.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:FA
OL,13,Fchangeable period with showers or
OL,14,Foutbreaks of rain interspersed with
OL,15,Fsome bright or sunny spells.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
